import React from 'react'
import { Card, Container, Form, Row } from 'react-bootstrap'

import './scss/issues.scss'

export default function Issues () {
  return (
    <Container className="issues-container">
      <Row>
        <Container>
          <Card>
            <Card.Body>
                <Form>
                    <Form.Check></Form.Check>
                </Form>
            </Card.Body>
          </Card>
        </Container>
      </Row>
    </Container>
  )
}
